1 will not openly recruit for the vacancy. Any vacancy for which an agency is openly recruiting
2 shall be posted on a website maintained by OSHR.
3 (b) Each State agency may determine whether a vacancy is open only to applicants within
4 the agency or currently employed by another State agency. Each local agency may determine
